    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さすがスリクス、三人揃った時の迫力は凄いな……\n……三枝さんから連絡だ。どうしたんだろう",
      "startTime": 10.6666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.9211113852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスの取材に日本からも記者が来てるらしい、か\nん？　その記者には気を付けろ、だって……？",
      "startTime": 19.1412495934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0461214782
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0461214782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "……で？　何よ、大事な話って\nkana、昨日のフェスでまだ疲れてるんだけど",
      "startTime": 29.9230598848,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3533.3347320999983,
          "startTime": 33.4563946169
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "その……三枝さんからこんなものが送られてきまして\n来週、週刊誌に載る予定の記事らしいんですけど……",
      "startTime": 37.9000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.8371875209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "何これ、kanaの盗撮写真？\nこの車に乗ってるってことは……会場に向かってる時か",
      "startTime": 46.0910642704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "……あの時はお父さんと大事な話してたのに\n尾けられてたとか、最悪",
      "startTime": 54.5577309371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.8007472119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "で、わざわざアメリカまでkana追っかけて来て\nどんな記事をでっちあげたっての？　どれどれ……",
      "startTime": 60.5577309371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9507471007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "……『ⅢXのkana、知られざる悲劇の生い立ち\n幼少期に母と死別、そして最愛の父に捨てられた過去』",
      "startTime": 70.1577309389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.8040803673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お父さんに直接インタビュー取りに行ったの！？\n一般人恫喝して、スクープ気取るなっての！！",
      "startTime": 80.1577309371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんのご家族のこと、好き放題書いてますけど\nこれ、事実ではない……んですよね……？",
      "startTime": 87.9333334287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.7050551815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさん、何か事情はありそうなんだよな）\n（たまに、誰かに見てほしそうなことを言ってたり）",
      "startTime": 96.6666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "は？　あんた、まさかそんな与太記事を信じたの？\nこんな安っぽい、ただお涙頂戴したいだけの記事！",
      "startTime": 104.9586889708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.7902703368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "離れて暮らしてたのは本当だけど捨てられてないわ！\n連絡は取ってるし、プレゼントも贈ってくれてたし！",
      "startTime": 113.4914491734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.9598834916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……で、この週刊誌はなんの恨みがあって\nkanaをこんなクソ記事の素材にしてくれたって？",
      "startTime": 122.4581143142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それがこの記者、むしろkanaさんのファンらしくて\n苦労記事が出ればもっとファンが増えるだろう……と",
      "startTime": 129.7666652362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.3694299304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "厄介オタクかよ、キモっ！！\n……kana、一人でずっと頑張って、成功したのに",
      "startTime": 138.1498415993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.2736026212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "それを今更お涙頂戴記事のせいで、会う奴みんなに\n同情した目で見られなきゃなんないの？",
      "startTime": 148.0310284515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.7224916701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "……ふざけんなっつの",
      "startTime": 150.7224916701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8665960634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん……。三枝さんに連絡して出版社に\n記事を差し替えるよう交渉してもらいます",
      "startTime": 156.5666652362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.4280019924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ、そんなことしなくて。どうせ無駄だから\n「これは正当な取材だ」とか言われて終わりよ",
      "startTime": 163.5060049773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どうするんですか……？\nこのままでは、kanaさんの意に沿わない記事が……",
      "startTime": 169.4999985695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.3356892431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、決まってるでしょ\nkana達で、そのクソ記事をぶっ潰してやんのよ",
      "startTime": 175.7854832411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.1181835815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "そうだなあ……週刊誌の発売日の、ちょっとだけ前に\nkanaの独占インタビューを公開ってのはどうよ",
      "startTime": 186.8854832411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "kanaが自分でちゃんと『本当』のこと話せば\n周回遅れのゴシップなんか、コケにされて終わりでしょ",
      "startTime": 194.0188165744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.7372765863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "ってことだから、あんたはまず\nインタビュー載せてくれそうなメディア探してきて！",
      "startTime": 200.2188165744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.1521499078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "時間もないし、中身はこっちで準備するとして……\nインタビュアーもあんたにやってもらうからね、いい？",
      "startTime": 208.1521499078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。……そうだ！　こちらのインタビューにも\nお父さんに出演してもらうのはどうでしょう",
      "startTime": 215.9999985695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
